dax_measures.Name: Correlation coefficient
dax_measures.Expression:
VAR __CORRELATION_TABLE = VALUES('D0_Data'[Date])
VAR __COUNT =
	COUNTX(
		KEEPFILTERS(__CORRELATION_TABLE),
		CALCULATE([Avg Price] * SUM('D0_Data'[Volume]))
	)
VAR __SUM_X =
	SUMX(
		KEEPFILTERS(__CORRELATION_TABLE),
		CALCULATE([Avg Price])
	)
VAR __SUM_Y =
	SUMX(
		KEEPFILTERS(__CORRELATION_TABLE),
		CALCULATE(SUM('D0_Data'[Volume]))
	)
VAR __SUM_XY =
	SUMX(
		KEEPFILTERS(__CORRELATION_TABLE),
		CALCULATE(
			[Avg Price]
				* SUM('D0_Data'[Volume]) * 1.
		)
	)
VAR __SUM_X2 =
	SUMX(
		KEEPFILTERS(__CORRELATION_TABLE),
		CALCULATE([Avg Price] ^ 2)
	)
VAR __SUM_Y2 =
	SUMX(
		KEEPFILTERS(__CORRELATION_TABLE),
		CALCULATE(SUM('D0_Data'[Volume]) ^ 2)
	)
RETURN
	DIVIDE(
		__COUNT * __SUM_XY - __SUM_X * __SUM_Y * 1.,
		SQRT(
			(__COUNT * __SUM_X2 - __SUM_X ^ 2)
				* (__COUNT * __SUM_Y2 - __SUM_Y ^ 2)
		)
	)
